node.text: creature of comfort 🦢 thank you @wacoalamerica for creating such an insane piece of technology that allows women to find a bra that *actually* fits them. bra shopping is my least favorite thing in the world because it can vary so often, but wacoal's mybraFit™ app has truuuuly made the world my oyster — j’adore! #thewacoalway #wacoalwoman #ad

node.text: a couple months back my dear friend @armannafeei and i sat down to talk about the music that has influenced me, the culture that raised me, and the poetry that came out of it for his podcast @areweonair 📡 link in bio — hope you enjoy :)
